Overview and Scope
We recognize the importance of protecting the privacy of personal information collected about you and other visitors (collectively, "Users") to our Site ("User Information"). We are committed to ensuring that your privacy and User Information is protected.
This Policy discloses our practices regarding how we collect, use and share personal information at our stores, on our Site, through our email and mobile alert programs, through other interactions with our customers and Users, as well as what information we may collect through any third-party applications or third-party sites, social networks, or social media sites (collectively, "Applications"). This Policy applies to your use of the Site, regardless of how you access or use it (the "Services"). For certain Services, there may be additional notices about information practices and choices. Please read those additional privacy disclosures to understand how they apply to you. This Policy also describes your choices and rights regarding the use, access, and correction or deletion of your User Information. By visiting and using our Site, you consent to the use of your User Information in accordance with this Policy. When accessing and using the Site, you may be asked to provide clear and unequivocal affirmative consent to the collection, processing, and sharing of your User Information via opt-in procedures.
Please read this Policy carefully to understand our policies and practices regarding your User Information and how we will treat it. By accessing or using this Site, you agree to the terms of this Policy. This Policy may change from time to time and your continued use of this Site means that you are consenting to be bound by the most recently updated version of this Policy. The disclosures contained herein serve as a Notice at Collection under the California Privacy Rights Act and other applicable data privacy regulations.
